{
  "macro_id": "landscaping.irrigationCalc",
  "domain": "landscaping",
  "name": "irrigationCalc",
  "inputs": {
    "squareFootage": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "plantType": {
      "type": "string",
      "maxLength": 40
    }
  },
  "reads_artifact_data": true,
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.squareFootage === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.plantType === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.inchesPerWeek === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.gallonsPerWeek === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.gallonsPerMonth === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.runtimeMinutes === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.frequency === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.monthlyCost === 'number'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.gallonsPerWeek)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.gallonsPerMonth)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.monthlyCost)"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "squareFootage": 1500,
            "plantType": "lawn"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "squareFootage": 1000,
            "plantType": "xeriscape"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {}
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "squareFootage": "Infinity",
            "plantType": "moss-garden"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": false
      }
    }
  ],
  "_note": "Pure compute, reads artifact.data. inchesPerWeek from a rate table (lawn 1.0 / garden 0.8 / shrubs 0.6 / trees 0.4 / xeriscape 0.2; unknown → lawn). gallonsPerWeek = round(sqft × inches × 0.623); gallonsPerMonth = ×4; runtimeMinutes = round(gpw/5); frequency = inches>0.8 ? '3x per week' : '2x per week'; monthlyCost = round(gpm × 0.004 × 100)/100. FAIL-CLOSED (fixed 2026-06-28): a raw Infinity squareFootage is truthy and the prior `parseFloat()||1000` let it through → Infinity gallons leaked onto the card; now Number.isFinite-guarded (Infinity/NaN/garbage → 1000 default, negatives floor to 0). IrrigationCalc renders ALL fields above EXACTLY."
}
